uk.co.strangeskies.utilities.tuples

Class Tuple<H,T extends Tuple<?,?>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.co.strangeskies.utilities.tuples.Tuple<H,T>
  • Type Parameters:
    H - The type of the head item.
    T - The fully qualified type of the tail Tuple.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EmptyTuple, Pair, Quadruple, Quintuple, Triple, Unit

    public class Tuple<H,T extends Tuple<?,?>>
extends java.lang.Object
    A tuple entry, parameterised recursively with type information for each subsequent entry. Currently entries must be non-null.

        public <P> Tuple<P,Tuple<H,T>> prepend(P prepend)
